Foreign Language School Set Up in East China
NINGBO , December 28 ( Xinhua ) -- The Huamao Group Company in Ningbo , a port city in east China 's Zhejiang Province , and the East China Teachers ' University , a prestigious institute of higher education in Shanghai , has jointly established a foreign language school here .
Construction of the 16.7-hectare Huamao Foreign Language School is underway , and 45,000 square meters of school building space will be completed before the fall of next year .
The school will have 50 classes and plans to enroll about 2,000 junior high and senior high students each year .
The students will have the opportunity to study English , French , Japanese , Russian and German .
